  .pusher
    .ui.masthead.vertical.segment.exdoc(style="background:#ddb98b;")
      .ui.text.container.introduction.exdoc
        h1 AKB48 Team TP fan-edited short video collection and distribution site (streamable only)
        .sub.header.exdoc
          | sub stuff
        .ui.hidden.divider.exdoc
      #semantic-sponsor
    #example.main.ui.intro.container
      .ui.dividing.right.rail
        .ui.sticky(style='left: 969.4px;')
          h4.ui.header Getting started
          .ui.vertical.following.fluid.accordion.text.menu
            .item.active
              a.active.title
                i.dropdown.icon
                b Preface
              .active.content.menu
                a.item.active(href='#using-build-tools') Using Build Tools
            .item
              a.title
                i.dropdown.icon
                b Installing
              .content.menu
                a.item(href='#install-nodejs') Install NodeJS
                a.item(href='#install-gulp') Install Gulp
                a.item(href='#install-semantic-ui') Install Semantic UI
                a.item(href='#include-in-your-html') Include in Your HTML
            .item
              a.title
                i.dropdown.icon
                b Updating
              .content.menu
                a.item(href='#updating-via-npm') Updating via NPM
            .item
              a.title
                i.dropdown.icon
                b Next Steps
              .content.menu
                a.item(href='#all-set') All Set!
      h2.ui.dividing.header
        | Preface
        a#preface.anchor
      .no.example
        h4.ui.header Using Build Tools
        .ui.labeled.button(tabindex='0')
          .ui.red.button(onclick="$.post('pointer/popIndex', {}, (res) => { event.target.parentElement.getElementsByTagName('a')[0].innerText=res; });")
            i.heart.icon
            |  popIndex
          a.ui.basic.red.left.pointing.label
            | 1,048
        button.ui.primary.button(onclick="$.post('pointer', {}, (res) => { if(res!=='!ok!') event.target.classList.add('red'); });") update index
        .ui.action.input
          input(type='text' placeholder='empty index')
          button.ui.button(onclick="$.post('pointer/addEmptyIndex', { tmp : event.target.parentElement.getElementsByTagName('input')[0].value || '!error!' }, (res) => { if(res!=='!ok!') event.target.classList.add('red'); });") add empty index
        .ui.action.input
          input(type='text' placeholder='streamable link')
          button.ui.button(onclick="$.post('pushVideo', { streamable: event.target.parentElement.getElementsByTagName('input')[0].value || '!error!' }, (res) => { if(res!=='!ok!') event.target.classList.add('red'); });") add video
        .ui.action.input
          input(type='text' placeholder='streamable link')
          button.ui.button(onclick="$.post('pushVideo/del', { streamable: event.target.parentElement.getElementsByTagName('input')[0].value || '!error!' }, (res) => { if(res!=='!ok!') event.target.classList.add('red'); });") del video
        p
          | Semantic UI packaged Gulp build tools so your project can preserve its 
          a(href='/usage/theming.html') own theme changes
          | .
        p #{ streamableVideoCount }
        p
          | For installing with specific integrations like Ember, React, or Meteor, see our 
          a(href='/introduction/integrations.html') integration guide
        p
          | For integrating Semantic UI tasks into your own build tools, or using a CDN see our 
          a(href='/introduction/advanced-usage.html') recipes
          |  section.
      .ui.large.info.message
        .ui.header Simpler Setup
        p
          | If you are using Semantic UI as a dependency and just want to use our default theme, use our lighter 
          a(href='https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI-CSS' target='_blank')
            code semantic-ui-css
          |  or 
          a(href='https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI-Less' target='_blank')
            code semantic-ui-less
          |  repo. If you just need the files you can download them as a zip from GitHub.
        a.ui.secondary.button(href='https://github.com/Semantic-Org/Semantic-UI-CSS/archive/master.zip') Download Zip
        a.ui.button(href='https://github.com/Semantic-Org/' target='_blank') View all Semantic-Org Repos 
      h2.ui.dividing.header
        | Installing
        a#installing.anchor
      .no.example
        table.ui.celled.table
          thead
            tr
              th Name
              th 年
              th Job
          tbody
            tr
              td(data-label='Name') James
              td(data-label='Age') 24
              td(data-label='Job') Engineer
            tr
              td(data-label='Name') Jill
              td(data-label='Age') 26
              td(data-label='Job') Engineer
            tr
              td(data-label='Name') 艾里斯
              td(data-label='Age') 24
              td(data-label='Job') Designer
      .no.example
        h4 Install Gulp
        i.fitted.icon.code
        a#install-gulp.anchor
        p
          | Semantic UI uses 
          a(href='http://www.gulpjs.com' target='_blank') Gulp
          |  to provide command line tools for building themed versions of the library with just the components you need.
        p Gulp is an NPM module and must be installed globally
        .ui.existing.segment
          pre.
      .no.example
        h4 Install Semantic UI
        i.fitted.icon.code
        a#install-semantic-ui.anchor
        p Semantic UI is available in an eponymous package on NPM
        .ui.secondary.menu
          a.active.item(data-tab='video')
            | Video
          a.item(data-tab='code')
            | Code
        .ui.active.tab(data-tab='video')
          script#asciicast-22121(type='text/javascript' src='https://asciinema.org/a/22121.js' async='' data-player='[object HTMLDivElement]')
          #asciicast-container-22121.asciicast(style='display: block; float: none; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; margin: 20px 0px;')
            iframe#asciicast-iframe-22121(src='https://asciinema.org/a/22121/embed?' name='asciicast-iframe-22121' scrolling='no' allowfullscreen='true' style='overflow: hidden; margin: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 698px; float: none; visibility: visible; height: 482px;')
        .ui.tab(data-tab='code')
          .ignored.code(data-type='bash')
            | npm install semantic-ui --save
            | cd semantic/
            | gulp build
      .no.example
        h4 Include in Your HTML
        i.fitted.icon.code
        a#include-in-your-html.anchor
        p
          | Running the gulp build tools will compile CSS and Javascript for use in your project. Just link to these files in your HTML along with the latest 
          a(href='https://www.jquery.com' target='_blank') jQuery
          | .
        .ui.existing.segment
          pre.
      h2.ui.dividing.header
        | Updating
        a#updating.anchor
      .no.example
        h4 Updating via NPM
        i.fitted.icon.code
        a#updating-via-npm.anchor
        p
          | Semantic's NPM install script will automatically update Semantic UI to the latest version while preserving your site and packaged themes.
        .ui.existing.segment
          pre.
      h2.ui.dividing.header
        | Next Steps
        a#next-steps.anchor
      .no.example
        h4 All Set!
        i.fitted.icon.code
        a#all-set.anchor
        p Well done! Semantic UI is now ready to be used.
